nodes.text: Fieler Dan was a Human female agent who served the Republic Strategic Information Service during the Cold War.

Fieler Dan was sent into the Justicars' Sector to try to locate the missing plans for secret tunnels running underneath Coruscant. When no word came from her to Coruscant Security Force Lieutenant Doorn, an individual was sent to find her. The individual found the plans and gave a copy to Dan so that she could pass them on to her daughter. Her daughter would use the plans to help bring in food and supplies for Coruscant's needy.
Fieler Dan appears as part of the "Secret Passages" mission in Star Wars: The Old Republic. The player can choose to not let Dan make a copy as a dark side choice.
